As a 54 year old Founder of an international project I have travelled the world and interacted with dentists on 3 continents. For 4 years I have been struggling with dental issues. Today Dentist Dr Smitha took an one hour to sit with me and work through various options involving possible removal of 5 molars with root canals, clearing out infections at areas where wisdom teeth were pulled, placing dentures and more.

Few things surprised me and I do not get surprised easily. First is the time she took. I have never interacted with a dentist that took 1 hour to sit with me. I felt valued and heard.

Second is her holistic approach. Dr Smitha clearly understands that the oral area, body and mind are intimately connected. Life style stresses have more impact than we know. I got great insight into life style stresses which have likely contributed to my dental problems.

Third is her commitment to the least invasive, simplest, cost effective solution possible. This truly amazes me in a time where many people are strongly influenced by monetary motivations.

I highly recommend Dr Smitha from Lalitha Dental Speciality Centre. After more than 5 decades I have found a dentist to return to. Have no doubt and experience the service for yourself.

I visited Lalitha dental clinic near Nethradhama, Jayanagar on the recommendation by my sister who had got her dental issues corrected. I had a severe decay problem which needed a root candling treatment. Upon initial diagnosis by the senior doctor, Dr. Smitha nagaraj handled my case, who is the best dentist I've ever seen. Her expertise at work, patience and the way to deal with the patient was extremely great and I was super delighted. I've got my other two tooth root canalled by another famous dentist in the country. But, the approach took at Lalitha dental clinic was extremely superb with highly sophisticated equipments and world class studio who has highly skilled doctors and technicians to work. 

And, this best service is provided at not at the normal cost. Both the service and cost are above par.. The complete root canaling treatment was done in for sessions and dealt with extreme care to give the precision at work..
 
Also, planning to take a tooth implantation and tooth shape correction. Implantation will cost around 35k per tooth. Not sure about the cost for shape correction. Upon checking the cost, will make a final decision and keep sharing my experience with Lalitha dental clinic.. If you want the best treatment in Bangalore, it's worth visiting the place from any corner of the city..
